    "description": "Welcome to the VR game experience that combines the fast-paced action of Beat Saber and the classic arcade-style gameplay of Pac-Man. In this game, you'll step into a neon-infused world, ready to carve your path through each level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game features over 20 levels across 3 difficulty's, each with its own unique design. You'll navigate through mazes while battling ghosts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith intuitive controls and immersive VR technology, this game is perfect for players of all skill levels. Whether you're a seasoned VR gamer or new to the world of virtual reality, you'll find plenty of excitement and challenge in this fast-paced game.  Unlock new weapons to use along your journey, and try to stay on top of the leaderboard for every level!",
